# compass-web frontend conventions

- Use the **App Router** under [compass-web/src/app](mdc:compass-web/src/app); prefer Server Components unless client interactivity requires `"use client"`.
- Styling: **Tailwind CSS v4**—extend patterns in [compass-web/src/app/globals.css](mdc:compass-web/src/app/globals.css); keep layout/spacing consistent with [compass-web/src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:compass-web/src/app/layout.tsx).
- Use `next/image` for images and Next.js metadata APIs (`Metadata` in layouts/pages) for SEO.
- Match existing TypeScript style (explicit types where helpful, `Readonly<>` for props where used today).
